HEADWORD: Proscript
<hw>Pro"script</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Proscribe</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A proscription; a
prohibition; an interdict.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who is proscribed.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Proscription</ent>⟦br⟧
